Every n1 Isa object At l
  Negative Article
    "inherited negative"
End Every.

The n Isa n1
End The n.

The n2 Isa object At l
  Negative Article "direct negative"
End The n2.

Add To Every actor
  Negative Article "added negative"
End Add To.

Add To Every thing
  Verb x
    Does
      "$-1$p"
  End Verb.
End Add.

The l Isa location
End The l.

Start At l.
  Say no n. "$n"
  Say no n2. "$n"
  Say no hero.